        <p class="text-red-700 font-medium">✗ Arrived without confirmed address. Couldn't register at gemeente within 5 days. Spent first month in hostel while frantically searching. Finally found room through Facebook group. Lesson: housing is the hardest part—start months in advance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

